          <title>
            <string language="en">Trumpets and Cornets</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Trompeten und Kornette</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Trompettes et cornets</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Trombetas e cornets</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Trombe e cornette</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Σάλπιγγες και κορνέτες</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Trompetas y cucuruchos</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">Trumpet and cornet are closely-related high-pitched brass aerophones commonly found in bands and orchestras.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Arts</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Trompete und Kornett sind die nah-in Verbindung 
stehenden hohen Messingaerophones, die geläufig in den Bändern und 
in den Orchestern gefunden werden.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">La trompette et le cornet sont les aerophones en 
laiton aigus étroit-connexes généralement trouvés dans les bandes 
et les orchestres.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">A trombeta e o cornet são aerophones de bronze 
high-pitched próximo-relacionados encontrados geralmente nas faixas e
nos orchestras.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">La tromba e la cornetta sono aerophones d'ottone 
aguzzi vicino-relativi trovati comunemente in fasce ed in orchestre.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Η σάλπιγγα και η κορνέτα είναι στενά συνδεδεμένος 
high-pitched ορείχαλκος aerophones που βρίσκεται συνήθως στις
ζώνες και τις ορχήστρες.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">La trompeta y el cucurucho son aerophones de cobre
amarillo agudos cercano-relacionados encontrados comúnmente en vendas
y orquestas.</string>
          </description>
